data.title: Destination Dachshund
data.content:
What does the face of NSW look like? At my place there are usually dachshunds in my face! ?

The State Library of NSW is asking you to take a portrait of yourself and submit it via Instagram using the hashtag #NewSelfWales. Your portrait will become part of an immersive exhibition experience that will be launched in their galleries, opening on 6 October 2018
